{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "茶馆瞎子李",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "茶馆·瞎子李"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "got_iron_box",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "after_box_1"
        },
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "heard_teahouse_story",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "first_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "too_early"
    },
    "too_early": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "老张那段都还没摆完。你娃耳朵都没竖起来，就先往我这点凑，学得成个啥子？",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "first_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "茶就免了，有啥子事说啥子事。",
      "next": "first_flags",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "first_flags": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "met_blind_li",
            "value": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "addArchiveEntry",
          "params": {
            "bookType": "character",
            "entryId": "blind_li"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "first_choice"
    },
    "first_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "learn",
          "text": "李先生，我想拜你为师，学算命",
          "next": "learn_1"
        },
        {
          "id": "help",
          "text": "没得啥子事，我就来扶你坐一哈",
          "next": "help_1"
        }
      ]
    },
    "learn_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "学算命？",
      "next": "learn_2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "learn_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "你是想拯救苍生于水火，还是看上了这碗饭好吃？",
      "next": "motive_ch",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "motive_ch": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "honest",
          "text": "肯定是想学门混饭吃的手艺撒",
          "next": "honest_open"
        },
        {
          "id": "false",
          "text": "救人于危难，济世于乱时",
          "next": "false_1"
        }
      ]
    },
    "false_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "放屁。你关二狗要真有这份心，城里头早给你立长生牌位了。",
      "next": "false_2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "angry"
      }
    },
    "false_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "直说嘛，你就是觉得这门手艺不费本钱，嘴巴皮一翻就能混口饭。",
      "next": "honest_open",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "honest_open": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "啥子都瞒不过李先生。我就是想混口比跑腿体面点的饭吃。",
      "next": "honest_2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "honest_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "这还像句人话。",
      "next": "honest_3",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "honest_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "命不是哪个都算得来的。光靠嘴巴皮，那叫坑蒙拐骗，不叫本事。",
      "next": "honest_4",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "honest_4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "你要真想跟我学，先看看你有没有这个命。",
      "next": "honest_give",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "honest_give": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "giveItem",
          "params": {
            "id": "iron_box",
            "count": 1
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "got_iron_box",
            "value": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "box_taboo_active",
            "value": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "showNotification",
          "params": {
            "text": "获得关键道具：铁盒子",
            "type": "info"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "honest_5"
    },
    "honest_5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "这个盒子你拿到，七天之内不许打开。要是七天之后它还是好好的，就在最后一晚带起它切渝都卫水库桥脚下来找我。",
      "next": "warn_ch",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "warn_ch": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "w1",
          "text": "这差事就恁个简单？",
          "next": "ask_warn"
        },
        {
          "id": "w2",
          "text": "为啥子不能打开",
          "next": "ask_warn_b"
        }
      ]
    },
    "ask_warn": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "简单不简单，要看你手贱不贱。",
      "next": "ask_warn_b",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "ask_warn_b": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "你打开试一哈，出了大事我可不管。",
      "next": "ask_warn_c",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "ask_warn_c": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "……",
      "next": "ask_warn_d",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "fear"
      }
    },
    "ask_warn_d": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "记到起，七天，莫开。到时候桥脚下来见我。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "help_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "人扶到了，嘴里头的话还没落地。你有事求我，脸上都写起的。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "after_box_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "盒子还在吧？",
      "next": "after_ch",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "after_ch": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "a1",
          "text": "在。你这东西到底装了啥子",
          "next": "after_a1"
        },
        {
          "id": "a2",
          "text": "我记到起的，七天不能开",
          "next": "after_a2"
        }
      ]
    },
    "after_a1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "你要忍得住，七天后自然晓得。忍不住，现在就能坏事。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "after_a2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "记到起就好。莫跟自己的命开玩笑。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}
